{"tid":1961700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［大家小心！］假冒入境處來電告知你被強制隔離14天","createTime":"2020-04-07T03:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T05:13:42.000Z","uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"25b2588a11b03a0127baebee02afb2581671ec2a","tid":1961700,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0rACUVR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0rACUVR.jpg&h=89da3c99&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JsWOg9b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJsWOg9b.png&h=92a7110a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VJhavuc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVJhavuc.png&h=d03b4c73&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcf3Qud.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqcf3Qud.png&h=22de793d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前日無啦啦收到呢個電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢係一段廣東話錄音話「你已經被強制隔離14天，如果有需要了解詳情請按「9」字與入境處職員聯絡。我都嚇一嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明我同屋企人都無去過旅行<br />\n<br />\n㩒左「9」字之後一聽到有個講普通話嘅人話自己係「入境處」就知係騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同佢講左佢英文問佢咩事之後就cup左我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢係咪歧視我係外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過提醒大家要小心，尤其是係屋企嘅老人家或者屋企人，因為可能佢地會好容易信、唔好講任何個人資料（之前順豐假電話明顯啲，依家佢講自己係入境處其實會嚇一嚇容易信左）"},{"pid":"6bb16bccb6b4c1aed6a54c70cf462974462a372e","tid":1961700,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"一聽普通話就知騙徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d31142e2682f71dae76acc761cb3a38bbda679","tid":1961700,"uid":205462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3wwiE0R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3wwiE0R.jpg&h=7f649720&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}